   <text>
      <body>
         <div xml:lang="en" type="translation">
            <ab>(1 H.) Germanos, quintanensis, to Haryothes son of Paourses . . ., greetings.  I have from you the quintana for Epeiph, 16 drachmas.  Year 11 of Nero the lord, Epeiph 21.  (2 H.) I, Germanos, have signed.</ab>
         </div>
